V1.4.description:
# **Requires a new Seed for AP**


## Logic
+ New Logic for Teleporter related paths
+ Cloister missing Bomb requirement
+ Snowveil village to the lower parts fixed
+ Swamp entrance to Magma pits reworked

## Client
+ Teleporter Randomizer implantation now available for both versions
+ A Controller error fixed which deletes your previous save file when starting a new game
+ Orb logic fix at generation stage
+ Controller error fix
+ Forcing "Free Roam" Gamemode on a New Game
+ new text at the top of screen after connection to an Ap world server
+ ^ shows an error message if locations dont match with local client
+ New console command to send Location to AP server
+ Sable and Celia now use able with a single Orb (normal shots only)
+ unlock every custom game mode when starting a new save file
+ Singleplayer seed generation should be alot faster now
+ Orb level 1 uses Celia and Sable normal shots when they are unlocked

## AP World
### Requires atleast Archipelago version 0.6.1

+ Added new Option Teleporter Rando, instead of normal Map transition you travel via Teleporter only
   currently Map transition are still enabled to reduce potential softlocks
+ Combined Teleporter, Transition rando and normal into a single Option
+ Fixed Location name groups
+ Universal Tracker works again
+ UT random Transition support
+ UT random Teleport support
+ (Teleporter mode only) Chapter 6 + all movement items unlocks Item and Orb crafting
+ New item group "Progression" to get the next Progression Item in Logic in your world
   (contains all upgrade items so it can missfire with vanilla upgrade)

##  Poptracker
+ Updated to work with Teleporter Rando
+ New Map images
+ New tab Crafting that contains everything which can be crafted

V1.4.4.description:
## Logic
+ Money blocks can be randomized
+ Purple / Yellow Shard can be randomized
+ Teleport to Morose with the Bed event  disabled when OpenMorose is not selected
+ Yellow shard is now used to upgrade Important Progression items
+ Shop Bonus is logically locked behind access to all Shops

## Client
+ Faster seed generation
+ Custom room near Tevi's home (not fully mapped)
+ Custom Text 
+ Boss Hp scaling fixed
+ Option to track Mananite shard collection (alpha), enemy kills and world location are currently tracked
+ Enemies do not scale off Attack Potions anymore
+ gain Tornado Spin when Dagger is unlocked

###  Shop Voucher added:
Shop Vouchers reduce the price to 0 in their respected region.

* Memory Box -> Morose
* Crystal Flute -> Ana Thema
* Frozen Fate -> Snow City
* Tartarus VIP Ticket -> Tartarus
* Valhalla VIP Ticket -> Valhalla


## AP World
### Requires atleast Archipelago version 0.6.4
+ Logic fix
+ A couple options to exclude Progression items from certain locations
+ An option to enable / hard place Manashard for tracking

##  Poptracker
+ Updated Mananite Shard locations
+ Money tracking
+ Unique Enemies (yellow shard)
+ Shop Bonus

## Fixes
+ Desert Base -> Entrance Logic fixed
+ AP Rabbit jump fixed

# Known Issues:
* Location "DreamKeeper - Dominator" - has the wrong region set and might only be reachable when the Dreamer's Keep wind is still active, which allows the Player to clip through the entrance blocks.

# Fix

## Client
* When a Shard was crafted the conversion check was triggered
* Unique Enemies could not checked if Mananite Shard from killing was received
* Teleporter could not be received from Money Blocks


### ID
* Cragmiester
* V_Guard
* Elite Mission E Magitite 

## Logic
### Resource
* added 4 missing Mananite and Magitite Shard each for Shop Bonus
* Bonus is now logically locked behind access to all Shops
### Money 
* Solennian Ruins - Money Room X: 20 Y: 13 # 1 -> logic fix
* Lab  missing Money added
* Travoll Mines - Money Room X: 6 Y: 9 # 2 -> Location Region fix
##  Shop Voucher added:
* Memory Box -> Morose
* Crystal Flute -> Ana Thema
* Frozen Fate -> Snow City
* Tartarus VIP Ticket -> Tartarus
* Valhalla VIP Ticket -> Valhalla

## Poptracker
### Moved Check Location to their corresponding Location on the in-game Map 
* Lab
* Plague Forest
* Swamp
* Dreamer's Keep
* Heavens Valley East
* Forest
* Travoll Mines
* Travoll Industry
